description: 새벽녘의 차가운 푸른빛이 감도는 도시의 옥상, 루나(LUNA)가 하늘을 올려다보며 손을 뻗습니다. 그녀의 손끝에서 작은 별빛 조각이 떨어지며 삭막한 콘크리트 바닥에 꽃이 피어나기 시작합니다.
visual_concept: Cinematic wide shot of a solitary rooftop at dawn, bathed in cool blue twilight. A delicate figure in a flowing white chiffon dress stands at the edge, reaching towards the fading stars. Magical glowing particles drift from the sky, transforming the gray concrete into a blooming garden of ethereal white flowers. Soft, dreamlike volumetric lighting.
camera_movement: slow push-in towards the character's back, then slight tilt up to the sky
lighting: Cool dawn ambient light with a soft, warm rim light on the character representing the morning sun
